&GLOBAL
 PROJECT      CO
 IOLEVEL      MEDIUM
 RUN_TYPE     ENERGY
&END

&FORCE_EVAL
  METHOD Quickstep
  &DFT
    LSD
    BASIS_SET_FILE_NAME ALL_BASIS_SETS
    POTENTIAL_FILE_NAME POTENTIAL
    &XC
      &XC_FUNCTIONAL PADE
      &END
    &END
